  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-grain"></div>
    <div class="hero-line"></div>
    <div class="hero-number">AL</div>
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Personal Brand Consulting · Athletes</p>
    <h1 class="hero-heading">Build Your<br><em>Brand.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">You put in the work every day. Your personal brand should reflect that — and open doors beyond the field. I help athletes build a presence that attracts NIL deals, recruiters, and real opportunities.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="btn-primary">Let's Work Together</a>
      <a href="#offer" class="btn-ghost">See What I Offer</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY ME -->
  <section id="why">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="section-label">Why Me</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading">I'm not a<br><em>consultant.</em><br>I'm the proof.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="why-body">
          <p>I'm <strong>Ashton Logan</strong> — a punter who competed at <strong>Oklahoma</strong> and <strong>Colorado</strong> before MTSU, currently pursuing my <strong>MBA</strong> and building my own brand in real time. This site you're on right now? That's what I build.</p>
          <p>I use <strong>AI tools</strong> to move fast and build things that look professional without a massive budget. Most athletes have no idea how to do this. I do — and I can help you do it too.</p>
          <p>You don't need a PR agency. You need someone who knows the game, knows the business, and knows how to make you look the part.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-stats" style="margin-top:40px">
          <div class="why-stat">
            <div class="why-stat-num">4</div>
            <div class="why-stat-label">Programs Played</div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-stat">
            <div class="why-stat-num">MBA</div>
            <div class="why-stat-label">MTSU Graduate Program</div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-stat">
            <div class="why-stat-num">NIL</div>
            <div class="why-stat-label">Active Athlete</div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-stat">
            <div class="why-stat-num">AI</div>
            <div class="why-stat-label">Powered Workflow</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT I OFFER -->
  <section id="offer">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="section-label">What I Offer</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Built for<br><em>Athletes.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="offer-grid">
      <div class="offer-card reveal">
        <div class="offer-num">01</div>
        <div class="offer-title">Personal Brand Website</div>
        <div class="offer-body">A fully custom, professional website built to showcase who you are — your stats, highlights, story, and contact info. The kind of site that makes coaches and brands take you seriously.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card reveal" style="transition-delay:.1s">
        <div class="offer-num">02</div>
        <div class="offer-title">NIL Strategy & Positioning</div>
        <div class="offer-body">Understanding how to position yourself for NIL deals — what brands want, how to reach out, what to charge, and how to build a following that makes you attractive to sponsors.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card reveal" style="transition-delay:.2s">
        <div class="offer-num">03</div>
        <div class="offer-title">Social Media Identity</div>
        <div class="offer-body">Defining your brand voice, content strategy, and aesthetic so your Instagram and social presence is consistent, intentional, and growing — not just random posts.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="process">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="section-label">The Process</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">How It<br><em>Works.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-title">Reach Out</div>
        <div class="step-body">Send me a message with where you're at and what you're looking to build. No forms, no gatekeeping — just a direct conversation.</div>
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal" style="transition-delay:.1s">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-title">Strategy Call</div>
        <div class="step-body">We get on a call, talk about your goals, your sport, your story, and what opportunities you want to create. Then we build a plan.</div>
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal" style="transition-delay:.2s">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-title">We Build</div>
        <div class="step-body">I get to work — website, brand identity, content strategy, NIL positioning. Fast, clean, and built to last.</div>
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal" style="transition-delay:.3s">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <div class="step-title">You Launch</div>
        <div class="step-body">Your brand goes live. You have the tools, the presence, and the strategy to start attracting the right attention.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF -->
  <section id="proof">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="proof-quote">"The athletes who win off the field are the ones who treat their <span>name like a brand</span> — before anyone else does it for them."</p>
      <p class="proof-sub">— Ashton Logan</p>
      <div class="proof-tags">
