        <span class="proof-tag">Brand Identity</span>
        <span class="proof-tag">AI-Powered</span>
        <span class="proof-tag">Athlete-First</span>
        <span class="proof-tag">MBA Backed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="contact-left reveal">
      <h2>Ready to<br><em>Build?</em></h2>
      <p>Whether you're a college athlete looking for NIL deals, a high school prospect building your recruiting profile, or anyone in between — let's talk about what your brand can become.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-right reveal">
      <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="contact-item">
